title: Looking to form/find 5v5 unraked/ranked team ~ chill yet competitive ^.^
body:
Silver 3 Top/Jungle main... Haven't really focused too much in the ranked area as I currently edge my way closer to 1200 normal wins... but I don't mind either queue ^.^

Just looking for a chilled and dedicated bunch of friends and players really as I am available most days and time and enjoy trying out things and having an overall good and competitive time as well... i don't mind any lane but I have stated the ones i am focused on and as such am not the best at any other role other than Top and jungle :p but I give it my best so if you interested hit me up ^_^

IGN~ MidNight Wolfy

poof.

hey man, im unranked wouldn't mind finding more friends that enjoy the game of league, competitive or even the social game.
